{"tid":322991,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發!)車路士出100M購希古恩被拒!","createTime":"2017-07-15T09:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T04:31:16.000Z","uid":44748,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f362d7a4306cbfb07d863c8186a129cf1bc26c14","tid":322991,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T09:18:00.000Z","msg":"TS: Chelsea &euro;100m for Higuain rejected<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/171717_b6df309ce094ff0382ccd6c1cb6f5de2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F171717_b6df309ce094ff0382ccd6c1cb6f5de2.jpg&h=8c8d4d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJuventus turned down a &euro;100m offer for Gonzalo Higuain from Antonio Conte&rsquo;s Chelsea, claim Tuttosport.<br />\n<br />\nThe Bianconeri spent &euro;90m to activate the release clause in his contract from Serie A rivals Napoli a year ago.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to Turin-based newspaper Tuttosport, Juve received a proposal worth &euro;100m from Chelsea this summer.<br />\n<br />\nPipita turns 30 in December and is under contract until June 2021.<br />\n<br />\nIn 2015-16 at Napoli, he shattered the all-time Serie A record by scoring 36 goals in a single season.<br />\n<br />\nLast term he bagged 24 top flight goals, plus three in the Coppa Italia and five in the Champions League.<br />\n<br />\nChelsea want a star name as their new centre-forward after missing out on Romelu Lukaku, who joined Manchester United instead."},{"pid":"4d98aa2841d8003a385f13e1225ec330bfd72e13","tid":322991,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T09:18:46.000Z","msg":"西瓜真係值100M<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0e48ba716df55119b12a5401bfd996e20179ad","tid":322991,"uid":10859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T09:22:37.000Z","msg":"肯出呢個價就唔會冇盧卡古啦"},{"pid":"e7a88532f472